---
layout: layouts/full.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
  order: 1
---

{% from "Card.njk" import Card %}
{% from "ExternalLink.njk" import ExternalLink %}
{% from "PostsList.njk" import PostsList %}
{% from "Text.njk" import Text %}


{% set postsText %}
  See <a href="{{ "/posts"|url }}">all posts</a>.
{% endset %}

{% set softwareText %}
  See {{ ExternalLink({
    content: "all projects",
    href: "https://github.com/olets"
  }) }}.
{% endset %}

<header class="container mx-auto space-y-12 md:space-y-16 lg:space-y-20">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-12 justify-between md:flex-row">
    <div class="md:order-last">
      {% include "nav.njk" %}
    </div>

    <div>
      <h1 class="heading-1">Henry <span class="whitespace-nowrap">Bley-Vroman</span></h1>

      <div class="mt-2 md:mt-4 lg:mt-8">
        {% set summary %}
          (pronouns he/him, pronounced {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "/ˈhɛn.ɹi blaɪ ˈvɹəʊmən/",
            external: true,
            href: "http://ipa-reader.xyz/?text=%CB%88h%C9%9Bn%C9%B9i%20bla%C9%AA%20%CB%88v%C9%B9%C9%99%CA%8Am%C9%99n"
          }) }}) builds things you see on the web, creates tools to improve other builders' daily experience, teaches and mentors at work and in the tech community, and strives to support safe, kind, fair, and welcoming cultures. At {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "Viget",
            external: true,
            href: "http://viget.com"
          }) }} he is an established Senior UI Developer ({{ ExternalLink({
            content: "bio and articles",
            external: true,
            href: "https://www.viget.com/about/team/hbley-vroman/"
          }) }}), and is co-chair of the company DEI Advisory Committee. Previously: {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "NMC",
            external: true,
            href: "http://newmediacampaigns.com"
          }) }}, {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "ReCYCLEry",
            external: true,
            href: "https://www.recyclery.org/"
          }) }} community bike mechanic and advocate, {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "Boston University",
            external: true,
            href: "https://www.bu.edu/psych/academics/phd/bbc/"
          }) }} doctoral candidate in cognitive neurobiology. Sometimes fiddler, publisher, and woodturner. Online as olets (pronounced {{ ExternalLink({
            content: "/oʊ lɛts/",
            external: true,
            href: "http://ipa-reader.xyz/?text=o%CA%8A%20l%C9%9Bts"
          }) }}). 
        {% endset %}
        {{ Text({ content: summary }) }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="border md:hidden p-6 rounded-md space-y-2">
    <div class="font-bold">On this page:</div>

    <ul class="flex gap-4">
      <li><a href="#latest">Latest {% if maxPosts > 1 %}Posts{% else %}Post{% endif %}</a></li>
      <li><a href="#software">Software</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="grid xl:grid-cols-2 gap-24 container mx-auto mt-12 md:mt-16 lg:mt-20 space-y-12 md:space-y-0">
  <section class="space-y-10 lg:space-y-16" id="latest">
    {% set maxPosts = collections.posts.length | min(4) %}
    {% set postslist = collections.posts | head(-maxPosts) %}
    {% set postslistCounter = collections.posts | length %}

    <h2 class="heading-2">Latest {% if maxPosts > 1 %}Posts{% else %}Post{% endif %}</h2>

    <div class="text-3xl">
      {{ Text({ content: postsText }) }}
    </div>

    {{ PostsList({
      classes: "sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-2",
      counterStart: postslistCounter,
      posts: postslist|reverse
    }) }}
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-10 lg:space-y-16" id="software">
    <h2 class="heading-2">{{ software.heading }}</h2>

    <div class="text-3xl">
      {{ Text({ content: softwareText }) }}
    </div>

    <div class="gap-12 grid mt-8 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-2">
      {% for card in software.items %}
        <div>
          {{ Card(card) }}
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>